{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8537494}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Por Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xB0; 226 de 6 de Febrero de 1996, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n, modif&#xED;case el numeral 2 de la Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xB0; 182, de 1985, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que autoriz&#xF3; a PESQUERA IQUIQUE GUANAYE S.A., para realizar actividades pesqueras extractivas con la nave &quot;Gualp&#xE9;n&quot;, en el sentido de se&#xF1;alar que sus actuales caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas son las siguientes:</div><div class=\"p\"> Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  2419</div><div class=\"p\"> Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  39,17&nbsp; m.</div><div class=\"p\"> Manga&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  8,60&nbsp; m.</div><div class=\"p\"> Puntal&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 6,50&nbsp; m.</div><div class=\"p\"> T.R.G.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 403,20</div><div class=\"p\"> T.R.N.&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 176,61</div><div class=\"p\"> Cap. de bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 599,00&nbsp; m3</div><div class=\"p\"> Arte de Pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco</div><br></div>", "i": 8537495, "v": ["MODIFICACION"]}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; Valpara&#xED;so, 06 de Febrero de 1996.- Patricio Bernal Ponce, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 8537496}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "numero": "226", "abreviacion": "RES", "descripcion": "Resolucion", "compu